Section 32: Useful Packages: Socialite Social Authentication (Social Login)

159 Introduction of Laravel Socialite

n addition to typical, form based authentication, Laravel also provides a simple, convenient way to authenticate with OAuth providers using Laravel Socialite. Socialite currently supports authentication via Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn, Google, GitHub, GitLab, Bitbucket, and Slack.


